room_title: Escape room "Roswell!" by EsQape It in Albuquerque
room_description: The U.S. Army has claimed that they have recovered a flying disk from a ranch north of Roswell, New Mexico. But have they? You have one hour to go through Colonel William Blanchard's office to find out the truth about the 1947 Roswell incident... before the Government comes and whisks it all away forever!
